These are Puzzles for 6x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 6x4-Level-2-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, mirinda, juice, iced-tea
There 4 different types of food: mango, peas, strawberry, kiwi
The people have 4 different hobbies: magic-tricks, collecting, chess, woodworking
The people have 4 different jobs:  paramedic, fisherman, software-developer, mechanic
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: country, blues, techno, metal
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: soccer, water-polo, badminton, lacrosse
 1. the mechanic is on the far right##1
 2. the person drinking juice is the fan of country##1
 3. the fan of blues is on the left of the fan of techno##1
 4. the person eating strawberry is on the left of the person eating peas##1
 5. the person drinking iced-tea is the person eating kiwi##1
 6. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the person who's hobby is chess##1
 7. the software-developer is between the person who's sport is soccer and the fan of metal##2
 8. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the right of the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
 9. the fan of country is on the right of the paramedic##1
10. the person who's sport is soccer is between the software-developer and the person eating kiwi##2
11. the person eating mango is on the right of the person who's sport is water-polo##1
12. the mechanic is the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
13. the fan of techno is between the fan of blues and the person who's hobby is chess##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |     3     |      4      |
| Beverage      | iced-tea        | mirinda       | juice  | hot-chocolate |
| Food          | kiwi     | strawberry         | peas     | mango    |
| Hobby         | collecting  | magic-tricks      | chess   | woodworking     |
| Job           | fisherman | paramedic | software-developer   | mechanic     |
| Music-Genre   | blues    | techno         | country | metal         |
| Sport         | lacrosse     | soccer     | water-polo  | badminton       |

