.:: Puzzle 6x4-Level-2-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, coffee, 7up, lemonade
The people have 4 different hobbies: fishing, puzzles, photography, drawing
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: disaster, drama, romance, epic
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: techno, jazz, funk, reggae
There are 4 different nationalities: chinese, american, italian, turkish
The people use 4 different means of transport: boat, tram, skateboard, car
 1. the american is between the person who's hobby is photography and the person driving the boat##2
 2. the turkish is on the left of the person watching romance movies##1
 3. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the left of the chinese##1
 4. the american is between the person drinking iced-tea and the person driving the skateboard##2
 5. the fan of techno is the person drinking coffee##1
 6. the fan of funk is on the far right##1
 7. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the right of the fan of jazz##1
 8. the person driving the skateboard is between the person watching disaster movies and the person who's hobby is drawing##2
 9. the person watching drama movies is the person who's hobby is drawing##1
10. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the far left##1
11. the fan of techno is the person watching romance movies##1
12. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
13. the italian is on the right of the person driving the tram##1
14. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the american##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |     3      |      4      |
| Beverage      | lemonade    | coffee       | 7up   | iced-tea |
| Hobby         | fishing     | photography   | drawing    | puzzles  |
| Movie-Genre   | disaster    | romance | drama   | epic     |
| Music-Genre   | reggae    | techno       | jazz | funk        |
| Nationality   | turkish | italian   | american     | chinese    |
| Transport     | tram       | skateboard        | car      | boat        |

