.:: Puzzle 6x4-Level-2-3::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: sprite, juice, fanta, mirinda
There 4 different types of food: banana, peas, potato, broccoli
There are 4 different nationalities: dutch, malaysian, french, canadian
4 different pets are kept: dog, hedgehog, snake, turtle
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: baseball, badminton, ice-hockey, motorbikeing
The people use 4 different means of transport: roller, motorbike, train, bus
 1. the malaysian is on the right of the person eating potato##1
 2. the owner of the snake is on the right of the person who's sport is motorbikeing##1
 3. the person who's sport is badminton is on the right of the owner of the dog##1
 4. the person eating peas is on the left of the canadian##1
 5. the person who's sport is motorbikeing is the person drinking fanta##1
 6. the owner of the turtle is on the far right##1
 7. the person driving the bus is between the french and the person drinking mirinda##2
 8. the person drinking juice is the owner of the hedgehog##1
 9. the person drinking sprite is between the person driving the bus and the owner of the dog##2
10. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the left of the person who's sport is baseball##1
11. the person drinking mirinda is the person driving the train##1
12. the person eating potato is the person driving the motorbike##1
13. the owner of the snake is between the person eating banana and the malaysian##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2      |       3       |    4     |
| Beverage      | fanta      | sprite        | juice | mirinda      |
| Food          | banana   | potato       | peas          | broccoli   |
| Nationality   | dutch     | french    | malaysian      | canadian  |
| Pet           | dog    | snake     | hedgehog       | turtle      |
| Sport         | motorbikeing | badminton    | ice-hockey        | baseball |
| Transport     | roller       | motorbike | bus           | train   |

