The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, van, boat, motorbike
 1. the person drinking juice is between the person who's hobby is singing and the japanese##2
 2. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the pilot##1
 3. the person driving the van is on the right of the person watching adventure movies##1
 4. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the person drinking juice##1
 5. the chinese is on the left of the person driving the motorbike##1
 6. the person watching adventure movies is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
 7. the entrepreneur is on the left of the indonesian##1
 8. the person driving the boat is the person watching western movies##1
 9. the person driving the bike is between the entrepreneur and the person who's hobby is biked-games##2
10. the japanese is on the left of the person watching comedy movies##1
11. the person who's hobby is biked-games is on the left of the person driving the bike##1
12. the electrician is on the right of the person drinking mirinda##1
13. the person drinking coffee is the person drinking coffee##1
14. the person who's hobby is camping is the indonesian##1

.:: Answer ::.
