 3. the person who's sport is rugby is on the right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
 4. the person watching sports movies is between the person driving the skateboard and the person watching adventure movies##2
 5. the indonesian is the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
 6. the person driving the skateboard is on the right of the person who's hobby is camping##1
 7. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the far right##1
 8. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the left of the person who's hobby is baking##1
 9. the person drinking soy-milk is on the far left##1
10. the person who's sport is rugby is on the left of the person watching mystery movies##1
11. the person who's sport is rugby is on the right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
12. the british is on the left of the person driving the bike##1
13. the person drinking juice is on the left of the indonesian##1

