 1. the owner of the turtle is on the right of the person who's sport is water-polo##1
 2. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
 3. the colombian is between the person who's hobby is singing and the fan of electronic##2
 4. the person drinking coffee is on the far right##1
 5. the person who's sport is rugby is the fan of ambient##1
 6. the person drinking water is on the left of the person who's sport is swimming##1
 7. the indonesian is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
 8. the italian is the person who's hobby is writing##1
 9. the person who's hobby is skydiving is the colombian##1
10. the person who's hobby is writing is the person drinking water##1
11. the fan of country is on the left of the owner of the fish##1
12. the italian is on the left of the person drinking cola##1
13. the indonesian is on the left of the owner of the cat##1

